CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 17, 1945, pg. 17, reads: "Keen Competition - The Belle Vernon Rens will invade the Centre Avenue 'Y' Next Friday with the determination to hand the 'Big Five' another defeat. The local boys have a different idea in mind.  The above photo shows members of both teams jumping for the ball in a recent game. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Referee throwing basketball in air, for game between Centre Avenue YMCA and Belle Vernon Rens, in Centre Avenue YMCA gymnasium
